        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[#长期跷二郎腿会让脸变不对称#[二哈][二哈][二哈]医生表示，跷二郎腿的过程中，人的髋部会抬高、不平衡，脊柱相应地会出现旋转和侧弯，时间长可能会造成脊柱劳损...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E8%B7%B7%E4%BA%8C%E9%83%8E%E8%85%BF%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E8%84%B8%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E8%B7%B7%E4%BA%8C%E9%83%8E%E8%85%BF%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E8%84%B8%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长期跷二郎腿会让脸变不对称#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>医生表示，跷二郎腿的过程中，人的髋部会抬高、不平衡，脊柱相应地会出现旋转和侧弯，时间长可能会造成脊柱劳损甚至变形。<br><br>长期跷二郎腿除了影响脊柱、腰椎，让肩膀左右高低不同，还可能让人的两侧脸颊变得不同，严重的还会影响颜值<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网）<br><br>不想变丑，现在请立马放下翘起的二郎腿<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hewm66nyc7j20c80c8aai.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
