            <title><![CDATA[【#杨梅用盐水浸泡后会爬出小虫子#，能吃吗？[裂开]】又是一年“狂炫”杨梅季。杨梅虽然美味，却有一点总让人不能放心吃下去，有人说，杨梅用盐水浸泡，总会爬出...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9D%A8%E6%A2%85%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%90%E6%B0%B4%E6%B5%B8%E6%B3%A1%E5%90%8E%E4%BC%9A%E7%88%AC%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%8F%E8%99%AB%E5%AD%90%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9D%A8%E6%A2%85%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%90%E6%B0%B4%E6%B5%B8%E6%B3%A1%E5%90%8E%E4%BC%9A%E7%88%AC%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%8F%E8%99%AB%E5%AD%90%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#杨梅用盐水浸泡后会爬出小虫子#</span></a>，能吃吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】又是一年“狂炫”杨梅季。杨梅虽然美味，却有一点总让人不能放心吃下去，有人说，杨梅用盐水浸泡，总会爬出白色的小虫子，如何解决？杨梅招的虫子是果蝇的幼虫，吃杨梅前可用盐水充分洗净、浸泡，果蝇会自动浮出来，再用清水冲干净就可以放心吃了。<a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91">@央视网</a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6pXUq9M" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
